        <center>
          <h1>My Favorite Recipes</h1>
          <p>This is going to be my favorite meal recipe ;]</p><hr>
          <h3>List of Ingredients:</h3></center>
          <ul><i>
            <li>Rice (paraboiled prefered) 75gr,</li>
            <li>Chicken breast 200gr,</li>
            <li>Olive or coconut oil,</li>
            <li>Vegetables of your choice 150gr:</li>
            <ul>
              <li>Tomatos</li>
              <li>Green beans</li>
              <li>Spinach</li>
              <li>Broccoli</li>
              <li>Cucumber</li>
            </ul>
            </ul></i>
            <center><h3>Steps:</h3></center>
       <ol><i>
         <li>Prepare rice and cook it in boiled water for 10 minutes.</li>
         <li>Chicken breast - all depends how you would like to serve it. Im prefer frying version; chop it on small (but not to small) pieces.</li>
         <li>Warm oil on pan and throw chicken on it. Fry it for 8 - 10 minutes. Use whatever ingridiens you like.</li>
         <li>Decide which vegetable you want and:</li>
         <ul>
           <li>Tomato, cucumber - just slice it, use some salt and pepper,</li>
           <li>Green beans, broccoli - cook in boiled water for 8 - 10 minutes,</li>
           <li>Spinach - fry it for 5 - 7 minutes</li><br></i>
         </ul>
